text:
We are currently just working on the DAML contract for an app we've built, but will publish for the Canton Network very soon.

Short App Description:

A self-service proactive analytics app tailored for non-technical business users that employs proprietary deterministic AI to specify desired insights using natural language. Beyond simply reporting and data exploration capabilities, users can program AI workers for real-time monitoring or scheduled analytics jobs. *Note*: For the highly regulated groups, don't worry we don't use LLMs in the model and will not have hallucination and error propagation challenges.

Enable users of the network with data visualizations & dynamic data exploration via Natural Language interface to view data associated with (but not limited to):
• Rounds
• Amulets
• Reward system
• Coupon system
• Fee system
• Synchronizer traffic purchasing
• Canton coin transfers
Proactive analytics platform allows:
• Users to subscribe to pre-built data alerts
• Users to program their own AI workers for monitoring & scheduled analytics jobs alerts (eg. cases such as determining the best times of days to mint and/or avoid synchronizer fees to optimize their transactions)
